WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.413 --> 00:00:03.439
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:03.439 --> 00:00:04.506
I'm sorry I'm a little late.

00:00:04.506 --> 00:00:13.920
We went to church, and as I was sitting in church, the Lord gave me an open-eyed vision about what we're supposed to be praying for tonight.

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:16.370
So, we're just going to jump right into the river.

00:00:16.370 --> 00:00:22.560
But I felt led to go over some of the things we saw yesterday when we were praying.

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:25.050
Now, we had two videos yesterday.

00:00:25.050 --> 00:00:37.920
Some of you don't know it; the devil interfered with our internet, and so we just kept going and we ended up praying until almost morning, which was amazing.

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:43.760
The glory of the Lord came in and hit me with Holy Ghost laughter.

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:50.680
And I'm telling you, I've never done that to that level on a live stream.

00:00:50.680 --> 00:01:01.383
And so it was pretty amazing—the Lord was just bringing refreshing, especially to me and to my son and to my wife, and just blessing us.

00:01:01.383 --> 00:01:07.330
You know, when you are in a place of always pouring out, it's nice to get refreshed.

00:01:07.330 --> 00:01:12.491
And when you get a touch from the Holy Spirit, it's refreshing.

00:01:12.743 --> 00:01:16.960
There's a lot of you that don't know about it.

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:19.017
And they say, 'Well, what is that?

00:01:19.017 --> 00:01:20.526
What were you doing?

00:01:20.526 --> 00:01:21.611
' That's just yielding.

00:01:21.611 --> 00:01:25.979
You can't make it happen, just like you can't make groaning happen.

00:01:25.979 --> 00:01:37.893
You get over in the flesh and you make things go and act weird, or you can laugh and be in the flesh, but I'd rather be in the flesh in church than in the world, right?

00:01:37.893 --> 00:01:42.440
And so you start out—it's like people say, 'How do you get over there?

00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:44.880
' You yield.

00:01:44.880 --> 00:01:46.770
You yield to the presence of God.

00:01:46.770 --> 00:01:48.686
You yield to the anointing.

00:01:48.686 --> 00:01:49.509
You yield.

00:01:49.509 --> 00:01:51.474
'Holy Spirit, have your way.

00:01:51.474 --> 00:01:51.863
Have your way.

00:01:53.191 --> 00:01:55.617
You are the potter; I am the clay.

00:01:55.617 --> 00:01:58.604
I am yielded to you today.

00:01:58.604 --> 00:02:05.806
' When a pot is on the potter's wheel and it's molding, the pot doesn't say, 'Well, I don't like the way you're pushing.

00:02:05.806 --> 00:02:07.369
I don't like the way you're doing.

00:02:07.369 --> 00:02:09.671
I want to be this way.

00:02:09.671 --> 00:02:12.114
' No, it's yielded to the potter.

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:15.779
Have your way.

00:02:15.779 --> 00:02:24.640
So, the potter's up there pushing here, and he's putting all the perfections out and doing all the things that he knows to do to make a good pot.

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:30.480
And if you are a yielded vessel, the Holy Spirit will make a good pot.

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:31.531
Does that make sense?

00:02:31.531 --> 00:02:32.819
I'm trying to relate it.

00:02:32.819 --> 00:02:45.493
And so when you're going over into the laughter and you're just yielded, and it starts out with you just laughing and you feel that bubbling up inside of you, the Holy Spirit will do it just like groanings.

00:02:45.493 --> 00:02:48.079
It's not something that you just fake.

00:02:48.079 --> 00:03:03.160
People go around acting weird and try to roll around in the aisle and mock and try to imitate something, but when it's authentic and you feel the presence of God, it's like Braden said: 'Dad, the tangible presence of the Lord was in our house last night.

00:03:03.160 --> 00:03:04.400
I could feel it.

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:11.440
' And you always wonder, because I don't want to be the only one having a good time.

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:15.096
When you're at a party, you want everybody else to be having a good time, too, right?

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:21.474
You're having a big party, you're celebrating, and Jesus is there, and you're the only one acting crazy.

00:03:21.474 --> 00:03:24.160
I'd say you're the only one in the town getting drunk.

00:03:24.160 --> 00:03:28.229
You're the town drunk.

00:03:28.239 --> 00:03:34.959
But whenever the Holy Ghost and fire is on you and everybody else is, it's like Acts chapter 2.

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:37.340
It was just the third hour of the day, right?

00:03:37.340 --> 00:03:39.919
It's just in the middle of the afternoon.

00:03:39.919 --> 00:03:42.000
'Are these men drunk?

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:48.239
' They're all thinking they're all wasted, but they weren't.

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:48.999
This is what this is.

00:03:49.379 --> 00:03:56.826
This is that spoken by the prophet Joel: the day of Pentecost.

00:03:56.826 --> 00:04:02.799
And I truly believe that Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:04:02.799 --> 00:04:08.427
And he's still pouring out his spirit on the church just like he did back in Acts chapter 2.

00:04:08.427 --> 00:04:13.000
I truly believe if you are a yielded vessel, we can walk in it.

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:18.720
And just like Pastor Candace, she was teaching tonight about Moses.

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:20.845
He was underneath the old covenant.

00:04:20.845 --> 00:04:43.759
How much more can we walk in the glory and be in the new covenant, the greater glory, and not just be somebody that is every once in a while visiting there, but somebody that lives there, lives in that presence, in that fullness of the glory, that people see it on you in these last days.

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:44.616
So, all right.

00:04:44.902 --> 00:04:46.760
That's what all that was about.

00:04:46.760 --> 00:04:47.540
Last night was amazing.

00:04:47.540 --> 00:04:48.260
I loved it.

00:04:48.260 --> 00:04:54.200
And if you haven't watched that video, I encourage you, if you just want to have a refreshing, to go watch that video.

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:58.853
As we were praying, the Lord showed me the revival again.

00:04:58.853 --> 00:05:08.570
And I saw Minneapolis, Minnesota, and I saw a well of revival springing forth out of the dirt.

00:05:08.570 --> 00:05:21.627
It started—do you know how you see cracks in the desert or in a big lake bed whenever the sun has dried up the water and the massive cracks are all in there?

00:05:22.373 --> 00:05:28.431
And you go, 'Wow, this riverbed is really dry and you can touch it.

00:05:28.431 --> 00:05:35.030
' But if you just dig down a little bit, the water is there.

00:05:35.030 --> 00:05:38.630
You just got to dig down a little bit.

00:05:38.630 --> 00:05:42.352
Well, the water table is always at a certain level.

00:05:43.984 --> 00:05:53.599
As I was praying into this, I saw the water coming from the fountains from the deep concerning the glory about what we're about to see.

00:05:53.599 --> 00:05:56.159
And the Lord said, 'Uncap the wells.

00:05:56.159 --> 00:05:57.599
' Uncap the wells.

00:05:57.599 --> 00:06:06.599
I saw the wells coming uncapped—what was, you know, when you cap a well and it was a springing forth of new water, new fountains of water.

00:06:07.999 --> 00:06:22.319
And all of a sudden, those cracks that were all in Minnesota started to fill up with water, and it was just barely touching the feet, just barely covering the soles of your shoes.

00:06:22.319 --> 00:06:24.770
And you're getting a little wet.

00:06:24.770 --> 00:06:35.920
But the Lord said, 'I'm going to take it up from where it's just on the soles of your shoes to ankle-deep, to knee-deep, to waist-deep, to over your head.

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:39.919
' And he said, 'You can't mess this up.

00:06:39.919 --> 00:06:52.606
You're not big enough to mess this up for what I'm about to do—the harvest of the prayers for the intercessory prayer that has gone forth.

00:06:52.606 --> 00:06:55.980
The seeds of prayer are springing forth.

00:06:55.980 --> 00:06:59.600
' And the Lord said to us last night, 'Watch this.

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:02.628
' And all of a sudden, bam, it was in Minnesota.

00:07:02.628 --> 00:07:04.200
Bam, it went to Tennessee.

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:09.760
I saw around Perry Stone's area where he's at, his ministry, springing forth a well.

00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:11.860
And the Lord said, 'Fill my cup, Lord.

00:07:11.860 --> 00:07:20.114
' I started singing that song, and the more I sang that song, the glory of the Lord started filling me.

00:07:20.114 --> 00:07:22.080
I could feel it.

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:32.937
It went from Minnesota to Tennessee, to Mobile, Alabama, to Fort Worth, Texas, to Oklahoma City, to Collinsville, to Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:37.410
Boom, boom, boom.

00:07:37.990 --> 00:07:42.320
And it went to Nigeria, and it started springing forth wells of revival.

00:07:42.320 --> 00:07:45.040
And the Lord said, 'I'm going to pour.

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:50.040
' And I saw a wave of revival coming out of Minnesota again.

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:55.306
I saw a wave of the glory of God coming forth out of it.

00:07:55.306 --> 00:07:57.370
And the Lord said, 'Pray for Mike Lindell.

00:07:57.370 --> 00:08:06.800
Pray for these people who are running for office in these areas, for Omar to find a new job somewhere else.

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:09.280
Praying for revival.

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:12.560
Praying for this major harvest.

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:17.380
' And I could see it going, and it was touching down in these cities.

00:08:17.380 --> 00:08:23.599
And he said, 'These are places of harbingers, like harvesters, like crop circles.

00:08:32.720 --> 00:08:35.700
I don't know how else to say it.

00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:49.769
There are glory zones—better glory zones, glory manifested zones, designated chosen places for the revival that God has put his finger on.

00:08:49.769 --> 00:09:07.325
' And when I told you I saw the hand of the Lord—five of it—all his fingers went out over the earth and shafts of light shot down from his fingers and made pillars of light coming from his fingers.

00:09:07.325 --> 00:09:21.223
And he said, 'These are the places that I have designated for a major harvest of souls in the last days in Tennessee, in these areas.

00:09:21.223 --> 00:09:37.240
' And there were shafts of light that shot forth, and there was major revival in America and parts of Australia and Asia and the Middle East, Europe, and Africa.

00:09:48.411 --> 00:09:51.830
And I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, as these shafts of glory came out of the Lord's hand, he said, "I designated these places.

00:10:08.427 --> 00:10:08.596
I saw satanic camps trying to camp themselves around and about these areas to try to prevent the glory from coming.

00:10:08.596 --> 00:10:12.594
But they're no match for our heavenly Father.

00:10:12.594 --> 00:10:20.050
No matter how big the devil tries to be, even on his best day, he's nothing.

00:10:20.050 --> 00:10:21.004
He's a loser.

00:10:21.004 --> 00:10:21.822
He's been defeated.

00:10:21.822 --> 00:10:25.314
And that's what I was trying to tell you all.

00:10:25.314 --> 00:10:29.725
Do you believe that God can make mistakes?

00:10:29.725 --> 00:10:31.928
Do you believe that you're a mistake?

00:10:31.928 --> 00:10:40.400
That God made a mistake by letting you be here for such a time as this?

00:10:43.739 --> 00:10:47.890
And that was my point in coming across last night when the Lord told me to ask them that.

00:10:47.890 --> 00:10:54.856
I don't believe that our heavenly Father can ever make a mistake.

00:11:07.876 --> 00:11:08.071
We are fearfully and wonderfully made, every single one of us.

00:11:08.071 --> 00:11:14.569
And we have been called to the kingdom for such a time as this.

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:30.560
And it's time for you, behind this camera right now, to get a backbone like a crowbar and expect the unexpected—to be expecting God to do something huge through you.

00:11:39.716 --> 00:11:39.947
It just takes one spark to light a whole forest fire.

00:11:48.630 --> 00:11:48.900
And he said, 'Pray for the revival.

00:11:48.900 --> 00:11:53.413
' And then he said, 'Pray for Elon Musk.

00:11:53.413 --> 00:12:00.852
' There's enough here even right now that we can pray that Elon Musk would have a visitation.

00:12:00.852 --> 00:12:04.640
I saw to pray for Elon Musk again.

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:07.519
He said, 'I'm calling him in.

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:08.280
I'm calling him.

00:12:08.280 --> 00:12:09.640
' Well, 'He's too dark.

00:12:13.280 --> 00:12:13.480
I don't know.

00:12:13.480 --> 00:12:14.293
He'll never.

00:12:14.293 --> 00:12:15.213
' No.

00:12:16.679 --> 00:12:28.079
The Lord said as I was being persecuted on Facebook, they told me they'd call me, and then they told me they'd call me again, and they keep giving me the runaround.

00:12:35.820 --> 00:12:36.080
And that's when I said, 'Lord, why is it the body of Christ doesn't have a faith book?

00:12:49.653 --> 00:12:49.876
Why is it that the body of Christ is always having to use what's the trend?

00:12:49.876 --> 00:12:51.520
Why are we not the trendsetters?

00:12:52.663 --> 00:12:53.349
Why is Facebook the leader?

00:12:56.819 --> 00:12:57.169
Why is Instagram the leader?

00:12:57.169 --> 00:13:01.360
Why is TikTok the leader?

00:13:01.360 --> 00:13:05.720
Why is the body of Christ not the head?

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:12.079
' And he talked about the money, because the body of Christ chokes on money.

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:14.212
You go, 'Well, we can't have that.

00:13:14.212 --> 00:13:19.707
You know, the love of money is the root of all evil.

00:13:19.707 --> 00:13:33.350
' But that's why I said you're ignorant: because the Lord wants you to have the exceedingly abundantly above all that you ask or think to be able to have platforms to bring forth the glory.

00:13:33.350 --> 00:13:42.1000
Then whenever we're able to say what we want to say and talk about Jesus where they don't say, 'You know what?

00:13:42.1000 --> 00:13:44.080
We're censoring you.

00:13:44.080 --> 00:13:49.371
' They turn me off like they did.

00:13:49.371 --> 00:13:52.880
'We don't like that you're talking about Jesus.

00:13:52.880 --> 00:14:04.389
Don't come back,' and they won't give you an excuse other than, 'We don't want you on our platform anymore.

00:14:04.389 --> 00:14:08.251
' Even with 70,000 subscribers and followers, 'We don't care.

00:14:08.251 --> 00:14:09.394
There's the button.

00:14:09.394 --> 00:14:12.280
' Do you understand?

00:14:14.293 --> 00:14:19.600
And then the Lord showed me, 'Why is it the body of Christ can't have a Facebook?

00:14:32.389 --> 00:14:32.617
Why can't we believe for that?

00:14:32.617 --> 00:14:36.571
' Mark Zuckerberg had an idea, but why not us?

00:14:36.571 --> 00:14:43.149
But it takes us to have a bigger mentality than always thinking of the one-eyed monster with the TV.

00:14:43.149 --> 00:14:45.199
And now the church is chasing TV.

00:14:51.566 --> 00:14:51.989
And I hate to say it, but TV's out.

00:14:53.908 --> 00:14:54.594
It's not the cool thing anymore.

00:15:00.777 --> 00:15:01.086
I mean, who watches Christian television very much?

00:15:12.649 --> 00:15:12.939
Not us.

00:15:12.939 --> 00:15:16.498
I don't know very many of the younger generation that does.

00:15:16.498 --> 00:15:24.103
Maybe a handful of them, but a lot of boomers maybe, but a lot of the younger generation—Braden, he goes, 'TV?

00:15:26.030 --> 00:15:26.520
What?

00:15:26.520 --> 00:15:30.035
' They don't even know about TV.

00:15:30.035 --> 00:15:32.980
His generation doesn't even care about TV.

00:15:32.980 --> 00:15:37.662
So, you're going to lose a generation for the cause.

00:15:37.662 --> 00:15:38.906
Do you understand?

00:15:38.906 --> 00:15:51.130
No offense to Daystar and TBN or whoever, God TV or whatever it is, or Victory Network, but I'm going to tell you, you're going to lose a whole generation.

00:15:55.459 --> 00:15:55.709
The boomers already either know or they don't know.

00:15:55.709 --> 00:15:59.620
But where's Generation X or the new AI generation?

00:15:59.620 --> 00:16:04.624
We've got to start thinking faster and be more effective.

00:16:16.285 --> 00:16:16.663
And that's what I'm praying: be more effective in these last days.

00:16:16.663 --> 00:16:20.982
Are you going to miss a generation for Jesus?

00:16:20.982 --> 00:16:23.520
What is drawing them in?

00:16:23.520 --> 00:16:40.080
When I was praying for Ericka and her ministry with Charlie Kirk, Turning Point, for the singing and the concerts and praying for things, how do we get the young generation to be engaged in church?

00:16:46.560 --> 00:16:46.950
I don't want to lose this generation.

00:16:46.950 --> 00:17:03.453
That's why even with the youth building, we're building this new youth facility because of the visions about the kids and the youth and the things that they're believing for.

00:17:08.128 --> 00:17:10.360
It takes somebody thinking outside of the box to reach a generation for Christ.

00:17:10.360 --> 00:17:32.080
And if we always think, 'Well, it's what the older people do,' then you're in trouble if you don't start planning now.

00:17:41.234 --> 00:17:41.600
And that's why I got so frustrated because the body of Christ is always thinking way behind.

00:17:53.640 --> 00:17:53.840
Well, we're chasing the TV and I'm like, 'No, no, no.

00:17:58.126 --> 00:17:58.423
You're off.

00:17:58.423 --> 00:17:59.360
This is off.

00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:02.440
I know it by the Spirit of God.

00:18:02.440 --> 00:18:03.520
You're off.

00:18:03.520 --> 00:18:04.880
This is not right.

00:18:04.880 --> 00:18:11.800
You've got to get on the right road.

00:18:11.800 --> 00:18:16.453
We've got to get on the right road.

00:18:16.453 --> 00:18:22.987
' And now you see, well, Facebook's kind of fading out, but what's the new thing?

00:18:22.987 --> 00:18:27.310
What's going to be the new thing to reach this new generation?

00:18:27.310 --> 00:18:29.314
Ai, but what will AI do?

00:18:31.460 --> 00:18:36.640
And the Lord said, 'If you pray, I will show you the secret things of that which is to come.

00:18:36.640 --> 00:18:45.129
What will be trending in two years, five years, I will let you be the leader of the trend.

00:18:45.129 --> 00:18:52.880
' But if you keep chasing the trend, it's just like chasing the news, praying over the news.

00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:59.386
Well, you know, I saw today that President Trump said the war is over and then Iran said this.

00:18:59.386 --> 00:19:01.999
'What did I tell you was coming?

00:19:01.999 --> 00:19:02.960
' No.

00:19:12.355 --> 00:19:12.551
What did the Holy Spirit tell you was coming?

00:19:12.551 --> 00:19:13.333
Not Brandon Biggs.

00:19:13.333 --> 00:19:15.180
I've got to get it.

00:19:18.189 --> 00:19:18.559
It's just bad vocabulary.

00:19:18.559 --> 00:19:20.978
What did the Holy Spirit say?

00:19:20.978 --> 00:19:21.490
'Israel.

00:19:21.490 --> 00:19:22.750
Pay attention to Israel.

00:19:22.750 --> 00:19:23.464
Israel will strike.

00:19:23.464 --> 00:19:24.640
' I didn't see America.

00:19:27.671 --> 00:19:30.133
I said Israel will blow up all their oil wells in the days ahead.

00:19:30.133 --> 00:19:31.360
Israel will do this.

00:19:34.730 --> 00:19:35.020
And anti-Semitism will rise up all over the world.

00:19:47.990 --> 00:19:49.016
Do you remember this?

00:20:00.540 --> 00:20:01.050
I didn't say America will do it.

00:20:07.547 --> 00:20:38.799
I said Israel will act alone and anti-Semitism will be at an all-time high against the Jews in the days ahead, and it will be so bad that they won't even be able to go to restaurants or to grocery stores without there being rioting and picketing and throwing rocks at them and things like that.

00:20:38.799 --> 00:20:41.691
It will be of biblical proportions.

00:21:00.680 --> 00:21:01.968
I said a new Hitler type of anti-Semitism—remember what I told you—will spring forth in Europe like it was in the Holocaust and it will be so bad that the Jews will flee and come back to Israel.

00:21:02.416 --> 00:21:03.536
I warned you of this.

00:21:03.536 --> 00:21:04.411
I saw this.

00:21:06.737 --> 00:21:07.102
It was a very detailed vision.

00:21:07.102 --> 00:21:09.760
Well, all these things are happening.

00:21:09.760 --> 00:21:10.960
Show them that.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:13.839
What is that?

00:21:13.839 --> 00:21:15.039
Trump's ceasefire.

00:21:15.039 --> 00:21:16.480
Do you show them?

00:21:28.036 --> 00:21:28.480
This is what the Holy Spirit said.

00:21:44.080 --> 00:21:44.539
So, we keep praying.

00:21:44.539 --> 00:21:46.251
We keep praying.

00:21:55.280 --> 00:21:55.480
So, as I was praying, I saw the wells of revival springing forth all over this land.

00:21:55.480 --> 00:22:10.331
And the Lord said, 'This will be a place of refuge to come and get a drink, and I will bring fresh anointing through your platform to bring forth where people don't have it.

00:22:10.331 --> 00:22:29.240
' You say, 'Well, I live in the middle of the country and we don't have a church like you're talking about and I've got to drive over 100 miles to go to a church like that because there isn't anybody around here like that.

00:22:29.240 --> 00:22:31.771
We're all dried up.

00:22:31.771 --> 00:22:38.080
' The Lord said, 'Be an oasis on the internet for people to come and get a drink.

00:22:38.080 --> 00:22:53.226
' He said it last night and he said, 'I'm going to as of now increase the anointing of the refreshing that will come through this camera so that you can have hope to get through your day.

00:22:53.226 --> 00:22:59.874
' Not through Brandon Biggs, but I'm telling you by the Holy Ghost.

00:23:10.048 --> 00:23:10.512
And I said, 'Lord, I'll yield to whatever you have for me.

00:23:10.512 --> 00:23:21.733
' I'll say whatever you want me to say, but I want you to drink from the well that never shall run dry.

00:23:21.733 --> 00:23:24.240
